Short:   *** Ultimate logical game - FREEWARE ***
Type:    game/think


Shortly about game:
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
	You have to collect all items and then reach the exit. Simply?
No! In levels there are teleports, mines and other traps. ;-)

The game has 6 world of different graphics and 20 levels per each one !!!

You can to create your own levels - simply and intuitive editor is included.
Press the Help-key in the editor to learn how to work with it.

This is only very succinct text so read the info inside the game and editor
for further information.


Requirements:
~~~~~~~~~~~~~
 - AGA chip set, 020+ processor
 - graphics and sound cards are NOT supported


How to run:
~~~~~~~~~~~
- from Workbench:
   click on game or editor
   - game tooltypes:
      LANGUAGE=<language>  <-- the name of file in pac2-locale directory
      NOINTRO              <-- do not show intro (switch)
      DBLPAL               <-- use double PAL screen mode in the game (switch)

   - editor tooltypes:
      DBLPAL               <-- use double PAL screen mode in the editor (switch)

- from shell:
   change directory to Pacomix2 root (no assigns needed)
   run game or editor with the same arguments as icon tooltypes


